metadata.name: Filigree lady I
metadata.description:
I create what I wish to be. And this girl is fierce and delicate. She's regal but humble, she fights for her beliefs and for her loved ones. When someone she cares for is in danger, there's a strength in her she didn't even know she had, that flourishes and takes over. 

This is a mix of a lady. I used to do jewellery, i used to do mosaics and mandalas, when little I used to draw women. That's where Filigree lady I comes from.

AI + Digital art
4000 X 4000px
